        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\nactor User\nparticipant \&quot;Bank System\&quot; as Bank\ndatabase \&quot;:DB\&quot; as DB\n\n== Login Flow ==\nloop until valid login\n  User -&gt; Bank: login\n  activate Bank\n  Bank -&gt; DB: validate credentials\n  activate DB\n  DB --&gt; Bank: valid/invalid\n  deactivate DB\n  alt valid\n    Bank --&gt; User: Login successful\n  else invalid\n    Bank --&gt; User: Login failed\n  end\n  deactivate Bank\nend\n\n== Transfer Flow ==\nUser -&gt; Bank: select transfer option\nactivate Bank\nUser -&gt; Bank: enter recipient details &amp; amount\nBank -&gt; DB: verify recipient &amp; funds\nactivate DB\nalt valid recipient &amp; sufficient funds\n  DB --&gt; Bank: account details\n  deactivate DB\n  Bank --&gt; User: show details\n  User -&gt; Bank: confirm transaction\n  Bank -&gt; DB: process transfer\n  activate DB\n  DB --&gt; Bank: confirmation\n  deactivate DB\n  Bank --&gt; User: transaction confirmation\nelse invalid recipient or insufficient funds\n  DB --&gt; Bank: error\n  deactivate DB\n  Bank --&gt; User: error message\nend\ndeactivate Bank\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="o3TCUol3wqtPbXXocofu-4">
